description: Waffle Pops food trailer is offering on the go breakfast favorites in a unique design, "Waffles on a stick!" The idea of putting a waffle on a stick to create sweet and savory    meals for any time of the day. The menu offers from a egg sandwich, chicken and waffles, to signature Waffle Pop combinations stuffed, dipped and topped with anything sweet or savory. Making them a hit with kids of all ages!
name: Waffle Pops
